\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl340\ql\qnatural

\b\fs42 \cf0 Preparation\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\sa240\ql\qnatural

\b0\fs38 \cf0 Combine the Cynar, St. Germain and lemon juice in a cocktail shaker, fill with ice and shake vigorously. Strain into a highball glass over fresh ice. Top with seltzer and garnish with the orange wedge.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sl300\ql\qnatural
